<HEADLINE>
FT  13 DEC 94 / People: Field Group
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Chris Simpson has been promoted to the board of FIELD GROUP.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Field Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
