<HEADLINE>
FT  12 DEC 94 / World News in Brief: Larsson's riches
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Sweden's Magnus Larsson beat world No 1 Pete Sampras 7-6 4-6 7-6 6-4, to
capture the biggest annual prize in tennis, the Dollars 1.5m Grand Slam Cup
in Munich.
