<HEADLINE>
FT  12 DEC 94 / World News in Brief: Children die in fire
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Three children were killed in a fire at a seven-storey apartment building in
Remiremont, eastern France. Another 18 people were taken to hospital where
four were in a 'very serious condition'.
