<HEADLINE>
FT  12 DEC 94 / World News in Brief: German terrorists 'to be released'
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
German justice minister Sabine Leutheusser-Schnarrenberger said she expected
several former leftwing Red Army Faction guerrillas to be released from jail
next year. This follows the release this month of Irmgard Moeller, who spent
22 years in jail for the murder of three American soldiers.
