FT  12 DEC 94 / World News in Brief: Search for sailors
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Poor weather conditions disrupted the search for 22 crewmen still missing
since the Ukrainian-flagged cargo ship Salvador Allende sank in the North
Atlantic on Friday.
